				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/C%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-mu%E1%BB%99n-to%E1%BA%A1/poem-edgha0TCk0BPP4LHreCsFg">Công đường muộn toạ - 公堂悶坐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-AqEVkg0YBflkFbuAXYlrbA">Hoàng Nguyễn Thự</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B7-Qu%C3%A2n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-%C3%A2m-quan-d%E1%BB%8Bch-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-zDYpEOCFii6cbxEepfmgKQ">Đề đồng âm quan dịch đồ - 題桐蔭觀弈圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B7-Qu%C3%A2n/author-qre_2HqJKAT7IbljC2mp1w">Kỷ Quân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Chi-th%E1%BB%8B-thu-ti%C3%AAu-ngo%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BB%87nh-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-G5eTtlYpaqKYUurHw02Fag">Hoạ Đông Chi thị thu tiêu ngoạ bệnh nguyên vận - 和東芝氏秋宵臥病原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%90i%E1%BB%83m/Ho%C3%A0i-xu%C3%A2n-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-07/poem-buof-7EiBbhE_L1-bSlIoA">Hoài xuân thập vịnh kỳ 07 - 懷春十詠其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%90i%E1%BB%83m/author-I2Exn1MHGlIYP0UMtUr4aA">Đoàn Thị Điểm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/L%E1%BB%AF-trung-khi%E1%BB%83n-mu%E1%BB%99n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-4DexrOQt_pi0plXJ7OMRnQ">Lữ trung khiển muộn kỳ 1 - 旅中遣悶其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author--2pwC2FLqv5BAX5uZnZLaA">Phan Huy Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Phi-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u-c%C3%A1c-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-l%C3%A2m/poem-4rbhaBWCV95XiuLjOqPcFA">Phi điểu các đầu lâm - 飛鳥各投林</a> (<a href="h